TEXT.S: = Takay = Gaga mniq Hwareyseyn Yurisyang ka alang Takay. 162 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 391 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 20% niqan 79 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 80% niqan 312 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Amis16%, Bunun2%, Tayal2%, ni rahuq na o1%.
